%F A394566 a(n) = (2^n-1)! / A002884(n).
%F A394566 a(n) = (2^n-1)! / (A006125(n) * A005329(n)).
%F A394566 a(n) = (2^n-1)! / |Aut((C_2)^n)|.
%F A394566 a(n) = A246137(2^n).
%F A394566 a(k+1) = a(k) * A001761(2^k-1), for k>0.
